  "description": "Ion quality — is the agent actually doing good work?",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Is the agent actually doing good work?\n\nCost tells you what a run spent. This pack tells you whether the spending was productive: how often tools fail and why, whether the same tool keeps failing in a loop (thrash), how turns end, and whether extension hooks are dragging on the hot path. A rising thrash index is the earliest signal a session has gone sideways. Every row links to the conversation it came from.\n\n> **No data on tool.failure / extension.hook_latency panels?** Those bind to Phase-B Tier-4 telemetry events. The `tool.execute` and `llm.call` panels bind to shipped Tier-1 events and will populate normally. All query syntax is valid."
      },
      "datasource": null
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Verdict",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tool failures",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "description": "Total tool execution failures in the dashboard time range across all sessions.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 5
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 20
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "links": [
            {
              "title": "See failure taxonomy",
              "url": "/d/ion-quality/ion-quality?viewPanel=6"
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tool failure rate",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 5
      },
      "description": "Failures as a fraction of total tool executions. Numerator: tool.failure (Tier-4). Denominator: tool.execute (shipped Tier-1).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.05
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.15
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json [$__range])) / sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.execute\"} [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions thrashing now (5m)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 5
      },
      "description": "Sessions where the same tool has failed 3 or more times in the last 5 minutes. The thrash definition from the instrumentation spec: same tool, same session, 3+ failures in a 5-minute window.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "links": [
            {
              "title": "See thrash leaderboard",
              "url": "/d/ion-quality/ion-quality?viewPanel=11"
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "count(sum by (context_session_id, payload_tool) (count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json [5m])) > 3)",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hook latency p99",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 5
      },
      "description": "99th-percentile extension hook latency across all hooks and extensions in the dashboard time range. High values mean extensions are slowing the agent's hot path.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 100
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 500
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "links": [
            {
              "title": "See hook latency by extension",
              "url": "/d/ion-quality/ion-quality?viewPanel=10"
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "quantile_over_time(0.99, {service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"extension.hook_latency\"} | json | unwrap payload_latency_ms [$__range]) by ()",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Evidence",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Failure taxonomy over time",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10
      },
      "description": "Tool failures broken down by category. Categories are the error branches in the tool execution path: permission_denied, not_found, timeout, parse_error, runtime_error, network_error, unknown.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 2000,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (payload_failure_category) (count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json [$__interval]))",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "accumulation",
          "legendFormat": "{{payload_failure_category}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stop-reason mix per turn",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 10
      },
      "description": "How LLM turns end: end_turn, tool_use, max_tokens, stop_sequence. A spike in max_tokens means the model is hitting its output limit. Shipped structured metadata, no parser required.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 2000,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (payload_stop_reason) (count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"llm.call\"} | json [$__interval]))",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "accumulation",
          "legendFormat": "{{payload_stop_reason}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Tool duration p95 by tool",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18
      },
      "description": "95th-percentile execution time per tool. Shipped Tier-1 structured metadata; no JSON parser required. Outliers here identify the tools slowing individual turns.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 2000,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "quantile_over_time(0.95, {service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.execute\"} | json | unwrap payload_duration_ms [$__interval]) by (tool)",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "windowed-stat",
          "legendFormat": "{{tool}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "heatmap",
      "title": "Per-tool failure heat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 18
      },
      "description": "Which tools are failing and with which category. Each cell is count of failures for that tool/category combination in the time bucket.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 2000,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "calculate": false,
        "cellGap": 1,
        "color": {
          "exponent": 0.5,
          "fill": "dark-orange",
          "mode": "scheme",
          "scale": "exponential",
          "scheme": "Oranges",
          "steps": 64
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "showColorScale": false,
          "yHistogram": false
        },
        "yAxis": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (payload_tool, payload_failure_category) (count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json [$__interval]))",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "accumulation",
          "legendFormat": "{{payload_tool}} / {{payload_failure_category}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hook latency p99 by extension and hook",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 26
      },
      "description": "Which extension and which hook are the slowest. Hooks on the synchronous path block the turn; watch for any hook consistently above 100ms.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 2000,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "quantile_over_time(0.99, {service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"extension.hook_latency\"} | json | unwrap payload_latency_ms [$__interval]) by (payload_extension, payload_hook)",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "windowed-stat",
          "legendFormat": "{{payload_extension}} / {{payload_hook}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Drill-down",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 34
      },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Thrash leaderboard (range)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 35
      },
      "description": "Sessions ranked by same-tool repeat failures. The session with the highest count for a given tool is the one most likely to be stuck. Click a session to open forensics.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Session"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "title": "Open in forensics",
                    "url": "/d/ion-forensics/ion-conversation-forensics?var-session=${__value.raw}&${__url_time_range}"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [
          {
            "displayName": "Repeat failures",
            "desc": true
          }
        ],
        "footer": {
          "show": false
        }
      },
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "renameByName": {
              "context_session_id": "Session",
              "payload_tool": "Tool",
              "Value": "Repeat failures"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (context_session_id, payload_tool) (count_over_time({service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "instant",
          "legendFormat": "{{context_session_id}} / {{payload_tool}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Recent failures with error preview",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 35
      },
      "description": "The most recent tool failures with a preview of the error message. Use this to identify the root cause before opening the full session trace.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "context_session_id"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "title": "Open in forensics",
                    "url": "/d/ion-forensics/ion-conversation-forensics?var-session=${__value.raw}&${__url_time_range}"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "footer": {
          "show": false
        }
      },
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "extractFields",
          "options": {
            "source": "labels",
            "replace": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "{service_name=\"ion-telemetry\", kind=\"tool.failure\"} | json",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "instant"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": [
    "ion",
    "quality"
  ],
  "templating": {
